snippet.title: Torchlight II Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description: The award-winning action RPG is back, bigger and better than ever! Torchlight II takes you back into the quirky, fast-paced world of bloodthirsty monsters, bountiful treasures, and sinister secrets - and, once again, the fate of the world is in your hands! Four new classes, up to 6-player co-op via Internet or LAN, a rich overworld and brooding dungeons. Available as a digital download on September 20, 2012 from Steam, Runic Games, Perfect World, GamersGate, GameFly, and GameStop. See http://torchlight2game.com for more.
